# Course creative knowledge

Index: **`data/research/course/KNOWLEDGE.md`**

## Hierarchy

1. **`GROUP_CALLS.md`** — live owner updates beat stale module text
2. Owner overrides: `PROMPT_BUILDER.md`, `VIDEO_EDITOR.md`, `APPEALS.md`, `PRODUCT_RESEARCH.md`, `BUBBLE_WRAP.md`
3. Modules 1–8 (`module_*.md`)

## When editing course files

- Owner reports group-call changes → append dated note to `GROUP_CALLS.md`
- Do not guess course rules — encode only what owner or modules state
- Do not merge dead strategy (Fix It Fast, Ms. Byte lane, InVideo, Peripheral) into course

## Module quick map

| Module | Topic |
|--------|--------|
| 1 | Violations — QC mandatory |
| 2–3 | Bubble / product research |
| 4–5 | Image + Kling video |
| 6 | Edit + caption |
| 7 | CTR ≥5%, misinformation words |
| 8 | Appeals |

## Research questions

Delegate **`knowledge-gatherer`** for briefings from files — `/knowledge-gather`

## Bot alignment

When course rules change, update bot enforcement if needed: `module1_qc.py`, `captions.py`, prompt templates in `.cursor/agents/`

Do **not** invent hooks or product filters not in course + owner overrides.
